-grc1:1037\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ El.\">El.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1037</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-grc1:364\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OT\">OT</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">364</biblScope> </bibl>; in implied questions, esp. after <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀλλά, ἀλλ᾽ ἡ τέκνων δῆτ᾽ ὄψις ἦν ἐφίμερος</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-grc1:1375\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1375</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg006.perseus-grc1:375\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Av.\">Av.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">375</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg025:283c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Hp.Ma.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">283c</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὴν Εὐρυτείαν οἶσθα δ. παρθένον;</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">of course</tr_> you know . ., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1219\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tr.\">Tr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1219</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n24506.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in prayers or wishes, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀπόλοιο δ.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">now</